🔍 Sidecar Debug Container - A🔒 Secure .NET Debugging (Volume-Based):
   • tmp-files                       - List shared diagnostic files
   • analyze-latest-dump             - Analyze newest .NET dump in /tmp
   • watch-diagnostic-files          - Monitor log files in real-time
   • show-diagnostic-summary         - Overview of all diagnostic data
   • convert-traces                  - Convert .nettrace to speedscope

🔓 Process-Based .NET Debugging (If Process Sharing Enabled):
   • dotnet-counters ps              - List .NET processes (most reliable)
   • dotnet-procs / dotnet-ps        - Show .NET processes across containers
   • monitor-dotnet [app-name]       - Live performance monitoring
   • dump-dotnet [app-name]          - Create memory dump to /tmp
   • trace-dotnet [app-name] [secs]  - Execution tracing to /tmp

🌐 Comprehensive Network Monitoring:
   • netmon [app-name]               - ALL network counters (HTTP+Kestrel+ASP.NET)
   • netmon-quick [app-name]         - Essential network counters only
   • httpmon [app-name]              - Detailed HTTP client monitoring
   • kestrelmon [app-name]           - Detailed Kestrel server monitoring
   • http-monitor [app-name]         - Basic HTTP client performance
   • http-connections [app-name]     - Monitor HTTP connection pools
   • http-failures [app-name]        - Monitor HTTP request failures
Version: 0.5 (Secure + Enhanced Modes)
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

🛠️  Network Debugging Tools:
   • tcpdump, nmap, mtr, iperf3, traceroute
   • netcat, socat, telnet, dig, nslookup
   • netstat, ss, lsof, arp

🔧 Application Debugging:
   • dotnet-dump, dotnet-trace analysis tools
   • Artillery.io for load testing
   • YAML/JSON editing and validation tools
   • Secure volume-based diagnostic file analysis

📋 Quick Commands:
   • debug-sidecar [host] [port]     - Full pod debug info
   • debug-network [host] [port]     - Network connectivity tests
   • envoy-stats                     - Istio proxy metrics (if available)
   • envoy-clusters                  - Istio proxy clusters
   • test-port [host] [port]         - Quick port connectivity test
   • test-http [url]                 - HTTP endpoint test
   • capture-traffic [host]          - Capture network packets

🔗 Useful Aliases:
   • listen = netstat -tlnp          • ports = ss -tulpn
   • conns = ss -tuln               • myip = hostname -i
   • netprocs = lsof -i             • listening = listening ports only
   • tmp-files = list diagnostic files • motd = show this message

� Secure .NET Debugging (Volume-Based):
   • tmp-files                       - List shared diagnostic files
   • analyze-latest-dump             - Analyze newest .NET dump in /tmp
   • watch-diagnostic-files          - Monitor log files in real-time
